        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/73ab20/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-12-06T17:41:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Bummer!  I have this problem all the time and have to make sure I\u2019m wearing my reading glasses when I pull a bottle these days.  Regarding 2011, a Gonon St Joe I consumed about six months ago was really singing with a couple of hours in the decanter, but I did make the decision to keep my hands off my remaining bottle for a couple of more years.  Cheers!</p>",
