        "created_at": "2019-12-06T18:23:46.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"156630\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Your note almost directly mirrors my thoughts on the Voge Chailles from a couple months ago <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/images/emoji/unicode/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>So it really didn\u2019t matter, eh?   <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/04707e6a7bbb03e0153e349d8a9270d30e1e9525.gif\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"[wink.gif]\" title=\"wink\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"156630\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ha- I saw that on Instagram and was thinking it was a little early to be opening that!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p><img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"156630\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I think it\u2019s a very nice vintage for Clape, just shut down hard.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>My notion, too, it was just so hard last night. Thanks for the input.</p>",
